one.co.uk\/collections\/wire-cage\">, wire cages<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/metal-holders\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/metal-holders\">lamp holders<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/wire-connectors-junction-box\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/wire-connectors-junction-box\">wire connectors<\/a> & junction boxes,<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/hooks-and-rings\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/hooks-and-rings\"> hooks & cord grips<\/a>, pipe fitting accessories, ceiling rose brackets, and hanging chains. Perfect for upgrading or customizing lighting in homes, offices, and commercial spaces.<\/p>"}},"faq_iJhDdF":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"How do I choose the right ceiling rose for my light fitting?","content":"<p>When selecting a ceiling rose, consider the design style (industrial, modern, or classic), material (metal, brass, or plastic), and the number of cable outlets needed. Our <a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/single-outlet-ceiling-rose\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/single-outlet-ceiling-rose\">Ceiling Roses<\/a> category includes multiple designs and finishes to suit your décor.<\/p>"}},"faq_TeXPFE":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"Are our lamp holders compatible with different light bulbs?","content":"<p>Yes, our <a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/metal-holders\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/metal-holders\">lamp holders<\/a> are compatible with standard E27 (Edison screw) and B22 (bayonet cap) bulbs. Whether you need modern pendant holders or vintage lamp bases, you’ll find suitable options in our collection..<\/p>"}},"faq_jPLkVX":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"Why should we use wire cages for lighting?","content":"<p>Wire cages are perfect for protecting exposed bulbs while adding an industrial or rustic touch to your décor. They are popular for pendant lights in homes, cafés, and commercial spaces.<\/p>"}},"faq_3UmUnT":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"Can I use these accessories for DIY lighting projects?","content":"<p>Absolutely! Our DIY-friendly accessories like pipe fittings, hanging chains, and lamp holders make it easy to create custom pendant lights or modify existing fixtures.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq_wMHaCR","faq_iJhDdF","faq_TeXPFE","faq_jPLkVX","faq_3UmUnT"],"name":"Faq","settings":{"heading":"Frequently Asked Questions","description":"","text_alignment":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":20,"reset_spacing":false}}},"order":["main","custom_html_ptWwbX","responsive_banner_Nkc6Xx","collection_list_qYWRJJ","shop_the_look_eUrTXn","gallery_688iyW","banner_with_text_QRDLYY","custom_liquid_BFCMza","faq_e3Mb4z"]}